title: Social media = broadcasting. Broadcasting ?= unnatural.
pid: 952b8adf-327b-47ae-9a78-91d72bcf4402
body: |2-
  It feels artificial, unnatural, relative to 
  being a species that processes socially locally.
  But I as a reader want to know the thoughts of 
  many people unwilling to communicate specifically to me.

  Sound is broadcasting too.
